/item><item>*************************************************************************</item><item>*                                                                       *</item><item>*  SetUp field SKIP_STACK = &apos;R&apos; to skip Requester step in Approval Flow *</item><item>*                                                                       *</item><item>*************************************************************************</item><item>  TYPES: BEGIN OF it_skip,</item><item>           doctype    TYPE /opt/doctype,</item><item>           skip_stack TYPE /opt/a_deskip_stack,</item><item>         END OF It_skip.</item><item/><item>  DATA: ls_index_data TYPE /opt/vim_1head,</item><item>        lv_value      TYPE /ptgwfi/value,</item><item>        lt_values     TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF string,</item><item>        ls_values     TYPE string,</item><item>        lt_skip       TYPE TABLE OF it_skip,</item><item>        ls_skip       LIKE LINE OF lt_skip.</item><item>  &quot;In</item><item>  ls_index_data = cv_index_header.</item><item/><item>  CALL FUNCTION &apos;/PTGWFI/CP_READCONSTANT&apos;</item><item>    EXPORTING</item><item>      constname          = &apos;IAP_SKIP_REQUESTER&apos;</item><item>      productcode        = &apos;IAP&apos;</item><item>    IMPORTING</item><item>      constvalue         = lv_value</item><item>    EXCEPTIONS</item><item>      constant_not_found = 1</item><item>      OTHERS             = 2.</item><item>  IF lv_value IS NOT INITIAL.</item><item>    SPLIT lv_value AT &apos;-&apos; INTO TABLE lt_values.</item><item>    IF lt_values[] IS NOT INITIAL.</item><item>      LOOP AT lt_values INTO ls_values.</item><item>        SPLIT ls_values AT &apos;_&apos;</item><item>          INTO ls_skip-doctype</item><item>               ls_skip-skip_stack.</item><item/><item>        APPEND ls_skip TO lt_skip.</item><item>        CLEAR ls_skip.</item><item/><item>      ENDLOOP.</item><item>    ENDIF.</item><item/><item>    READ TABLE lt_skip INTO ls_skip</item><item>      WITH KEY doctype = ls_index_data-doctype.</item><item>    IF sy-subrc EQ 0.</item><item>      ls_index_data-skip_stack = ls_skip-skip_stack.</item><item/><item>    ELSE.</item><item>      CLEAR ls_index_data-skip_stack.</item><item/><item>    ENDIF.</item><item/><item>  ELSE.</item><item>    CLEAR ls_index_data-skip_stack.</item><item/><item>  ENDIF.</item><item/><item>  &quot;Out</item><item>  cv_index_header = ls_index_data.</item><item/><item>  ev_success = &apos;X&apos;.</item><item/><item>ENDMETHOD.</item></_-OPT_-IF_D_BP_MODULE_--7EPROCESSING></METHOD_SOURCE></CLASS_ROOT>